snippet.title: S8E6 | Virender Sehwag | Breakfast with Champions ft Gaurav Kapur | @skodaindia     ‚Äã
snippet.description:
The season finale of ≈†KODA presents Breakfast with Champions ft. Gaurav Kapur has some royal swag! üèèüåü Say hello to The Nawab of Najafgarh, The Sultan of Multan. üëë

Virender Sehwag is a born entertainer and he continues to enthrall us with his take on his teammates and stories that are now cricketing folklore. From scooter rides with Ashish Nehra to pranking Sourav Ganguly, and from farm fresh buffalo milk to fine dining that Sachin introduced him to, this episode is a rollercoaster of laughter and nostalgia. 

Hear all about his banter with Shoaib Akhtar and the love he got from Pakistani shopkeepers, the invaluable advice Tiger Pataudi's gave him, how he had to return from the airport before his debut and the epic moment he scored 300 runs with a sensational six! 

This episode tastes best with garma-garam desi ghee ke Chole Bhature with Lassi in a kulhad.

Episode 3788: Pyarelal's Dilemma
--------------------------------------------------------
Pyaarelal gets into trouble as Sapna and Kalpana have accepted his proposal to get married. Earlier Sapna had not revealed her decision while Babita and Madhavi had asked Pyaarelal to accept Kalpana. As everyone discusses the matter at Popatlal's house, Dr. Hathi comes excited to his house. he announces that they have brought him another proposal for marriage. Anjali and Taarak discuss who will tell the truth to Sapna's family, he calls Sapna's mother but she thinks it to be a prank. Keep an eye out!

Team Drishti wishes Suraj a very successful and fruitful career.

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal‚Äôs Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

snippet.title: Tere Bin Ep 50 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 50 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 1st June 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma

Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

Sambhavna Seth‚Äôs full name is Sambhavna Surender Kumar Seth. We must have seen her on YouTube, in Big Boss, and in many bhojpuri songs. She had a lot of love for dance since childhood. From the very beginning, she wanted to become a heroine. To make a career, she went to Mumbai with her father and gave many auditions, but did not get work and came back to Delhi. She did not do any work for 1 year, then after gaining some confidence, she again came to Mumbai. Got a film after a lot of struggle. She has worked in songs of many big films but those songs did not become hits but everyone was quite impressed with her dance.
Then he got a chance to work in Bhojpuri songs. The first song became so famous that now she started getting a lot of work in the Bhojpuri industry. Time passed and she also appeared in many reality shows like Big Boss, Khatron ke khiladi and Desi Girl. Today she runs a YouTube channel named Sambhavna Seth Entertainment on which she posts vlogs.

Today Sambhavna will tell her life story through Josh Talks. So definitely watch this Hindi motivational video of Josh Talks.

snippet.title: The Hustle Reunion song , MTV Hustle 03 , Audition starts now
snippet.description:
MTV Hustle returns with auditions for its next season. 
Your favourite rappers from Hustle 2.0 reunite to bring to you The Hustle Reunion song which is a celebration of their journey on season 2 of Hustle.  
And now it‚Äôs your chance to be a part of the next season of your favourite rap show. So come on, vibe on this banger with MC Square, Paradox, Gravity, Srushti Tawade, Wicked Sunny, Nazz, Spectra & Panther as they celebrate the magic of Hustle. 

India, Ab Tumhari Baari! Tayyar ho jao for the auditions of MTV Hustle 03- Represent.

Track: The Hustle Reunion 
Written and Performed by: @mc_square7000   @Paradoxhere  @gravitymusic  @Srushti_Tawade  @nazzmusic  @spectra_music  @buildingpanther  Wicked Sunny 
Additional Lyricis: @epriyer  
Composers: @ParimalShais 
Mix & Master- Kalmireddy Nikhil

For more updates, follow this season of Hustle on:
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/mtvhustle/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/mtvhustle
Twitter: https://twitter.com/mtvhustle?s=20

#MTVHustle03 #HustleRepresent #HustleShunyaTeen #Hustlers #Hustle #MTVHustle
------------------------------

Lyrics 
 
SRUSHTI

Magazine me photo, check!
Mere naam ka logo, check!
Jab Hustle me dhoom machaake nikli toh
All India Solo, check!
Stage to Bollywood to Times Square!
That's jolly good!
And if you still don't know ke main nahin toh kaun, you really should!


WICKED SUNNY

Ek loose t-shirt 
Sar pe hai cap
Hobby aur passion 
Yeh dono hi rap
Hustle se mil gaya
Bada wala break
Koi bole mujhe sexy
Aur koi bole bhai mujhe
Dubai ka Sheikh

Hustle ke baad maine khel diya FIFA
Ban gaya Roadie aur likh diya Splitsvilla
MTV sasural waale khush hai kaafi
Unhein mere jaisa sexy damaad milaa!

PARADOX

Kara maine Hustle hard
Tabhi mujhe mila bhar bhar ke pyaar 
Najafgarh ka doosra nawaab 
Mila khitaab mila ghar ghar se pyaar
Supersonic Super Shows
Super Car seedha MTV ke baad
Super Power Super Skills
Super Hip Hop 
Sabse upar Hip Hop

MC SQUARE

Hustle mein hahakaar hoonk bhari
Naam te Lambardar achook
Dhari ek taang khidki te bahar
Dooji Angad ban
Rap Game mein kood padi
Dole tha 4 baje pahle 4 reh gaya paache haa
Star pahle bas aasma mein ib star rah gaye paache maa!

Ko leke aage badhe
WON'T STOP
Kalam humari chale
HARD WORK
Hustle se Haasil karke dikhaya humne

HARD WORK

Hustle ka buzzer baja, dagar bana
Safar chala
Hunar se diya issteefa
Kalam ka mera aisa asar raha ke
Noida ka ladka maano ho Mustafa

Ab Hustle hai maano meri Agneepath
Iss Agneepath ka main Rauf Lala
Hateron ke munh pe bolu ""Na"" jaise 
Shehar Bombay ka autowala

PANTHER

Paer phailata hoon baahar main chaadar ke
Baap ka naam liya karo aadar se
Itihaas Hometown Show mein aaye banakar hum
Poora desh bola saath Vande Mataram

Fir TV pe Hustle kar badle zamaane aise

Lokal jo chali, na gaadi ruki
Ab King Grav bana King Kong
Yeh na sing-song, real Hip-Hop!

snippet.title: Meet India's Most RESPECTED Politician - Nitin Gadkari On Figuring Out 93 | Raj Shamani
snippet.description:
Co-presented to you by @MyGovIndia 

Order my first book 'Build, Don't Talk' here: https://amzn.eu/d/eCfijRu

https://www.youtube.com/@rajshamaniclips

https://www.youtube.com/@RajShamani.Shorts

--------------

Join us for an insightful conversation with Nitin Gadkari, an esteemed Indian politician and the current Minister of Road Transport and Highways of India, on our latest podcast episode! üåü

In this engaging discussion, we delve into Mr. Gadkari's visionary approach to infrastructure development, sustainable transportation, and his unwavering commitment to transforming India's road network. As one of the key architects behind numerous ambitious projects, he shares valuable insights on building world-class highways, promoting electric mobility, and implementing innovative solutions to tackle the challenges of urban congestion and pollution.

Get ready to gain a deeper understanding of the transformative initiatives spearheaded by Mr. Gadkari, as he discusses the significance of renewable energy in transportation, the integration of smart technologies, and the promotion of alternative fuels. Discover how his innovative thinking and strategic planning are paving the way for a greener, more efficient, and digitally connected India.

Beyond infrastructure, we explore Mr. Gadkari's broader vision for economic growth, job creation, and the development of rural areas. Join us for this inspiring conversation with Nitin Gadkari, a dynamic leader who is shaping the future of India's transportation landscape. Tune in to gain valuable insights and be part of the journey towards a sustainable and prosperous nation. Don't miss out - subscribe to our channel and hit the notification bell to stay updated with our latest episodes!

ùêÉùêöùê≤ ùüë:
Normal Wheat Flour Chapati
ùêÉùêöùê≤ ùüí:
* Rice flour (‡§ö‡§æ‡§µ‡§≤ ‡§ï‡§æ ‡§Ü‡§ü‡§æ) - 1 Cup

ùêÉùêöùê≤ ùüì:
* Rice

Mix well, cover & keep it for 5 minutes. Then knead the dough well else there will be cracks while patting roti. Finally, make chapati & enjoy with Dal, Bhindi, Curd & Sproud Salad. 

ùêÉùêöùê≤ ùüê - ùêÖùê®ùê´ ùêëùêöùê†ùê¢ ùêèùêöùê´ùêöùê≠ùê°ùêö, keep the pan on the flame & put Water & come to boil first. When the Water is boiled then put Ragi Atta & mix. Mix well, cover & keep it for 5 minutes. Then knead the dough well else there will be cracks while patting roti. Finally, make chapati & enjoy with Sabzi, Mango, Papad & Sproud Raita. 

ùêÉùêöùê≤ ùüí - ùêÖùê®ùê´ ùêëùê¢ùêúùêû, wash some Rice and put it in pressure cooker. Add two cups of water along with a few drops of Oil/Ghee & Salt to it. 
Turn the heat to high. Wait for 3 steams and turn off the heat & release the pressure. Serve hot & enjoy with Chhole, Salad, Curd & Dry Arbi ki sabzi. 

ùêÉùêöùê≤ ùüì - ùêÖùê®ùê´ ùêåùêÆùê•ùê≠ùê¢ùê†ùê´ùêöùê¢ùêß ùêëùê®ùê≠ùê¢, take a plate & put some Multigrain Flour & bind the dough by adding some water gradually. Mix well, cover & keep it for 5 minutes. Then knead the dough well else there will be cracks while patting roti. Finally, make chapati & enjoy with Dal, Bhindi, Curd & Sproud Salad. 

ùêÉùêöùê≤ ùüê - ùêÖùê®ùê´ ùêëùêöùê†ùê¢ ùêèùêöùê´ùêöùê≠ùê°ùêö, keep the pan on the flame & put Water & come to boil first. When the Water is boiled then put Ragi Atta & mix. Roast the Paratha & serve the Healthy Ragi Tawa Paratha Recipe along with Mix Dal, Dry Karele, Raita & Green Salad. 

ùêÉùêöùê≤ ùüë - ùêÖùê®ùê´ ùêëùê¢ùêúùêû ùêëùê®ùê≠ùê¢, keep the pan on the flame & put Water & come to boil first. When the Water boiled then put Rice Flour. Mix well, cover & keep it for 5 minutes. Then knead the dough well else there will be cracks while patting roti. Finally, make chapati & enjoy with Sabzi, Mango, Papad & Sproud Raita. 

ùêÉùêöùê≤ ùüí - ùêÖùê®ùê´ ùêëùê¢ùêúùêû, wash some Rice and put it in pressure cooker. Add two cups of water along with a few drops of Oil/Ghee & Salt to it.

snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3786: Sapna Ya Kalpana?
--------------------------------------------------------
Pyaarelal, according to the astrologer, must choose his bride before 6 p.m. since it is a fortunate period for him. So Pyaarelal proclaims that he likes Sapna, and everyone waits for Sapna's response. The doorbell rings, and Taarak looks through the peephole to see if Alka and her parents have arrived. Sapna's parents interrogate them about the truth, and Taarak informs them. Sapna's parents are first upset, but when Anjali explains that the marriage bureau contacted them after their meeting was scheduled, they accept the situation. What happens next? Which girl will become Pyaarelal's bride?
 
Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3786, 1 June 2023

*About* 
------------

               Yeh kahani hai ek sanyukt parivaar mai rehnewale Modi khaandaan ki. Izzatdaar, ameer aur naamcheen hone ke bawajud, ghar ke sanskaar aur sanskriti hain inka saccha dhan. Iss ghar ko chalati hai choti bahu, Kokilaben jissey darte hain saare sadasya. Kokilaben ke bade bete, Ahem ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi se joh hai ek saaf dil ki siddhi saadhi, anpapdh ladki. Unke jethani ke bete, Jigar ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi ki behen, Raashi se joh hai bohot hi chaalaak aur nakhrel. 
              Raashi hamesha dikhati hai neecha Gopi ko aur karti hai uske liye mushkilen taiyaar. Par Gopi ka haath thama Kokilaben ne aur banaya ussey hoshiyaar. Iss saas-bahu ki jodi ne apne pyaar, dulaar aur balidaan se bandhe rakha hai Modi parivaar ko.

snippet.title: Debt ceiling explained in Hindi | American Economic Crisis | Abhi and Niyu
snippet.description:
In this video, Abhi and Niyu explain the Debt Ceiling crisis of USA and why America will never be like Sri Lanka.

#debtceiling #worldaffairs #abhiandniyu 

In our informative and engaging video, "Understanding the Debt Ceiling: Navigating Fiscal Challenges," we delve into one of the most critical aspects of economic governance: the debt ceiling. Join us on a journey through the complexities of national debt, government spending, and the mechanisms in place to manage these fiscal challenges.

With a clear and concise narrative, we break down the debt ceiling concept, explaining its purpose and implications. Our expert hosts provide a comprehensive overview of how the debt ceiling functions within the framework of a country's financial system and explore the practical effects it has on government operations and the economy at large.

As the video progresses, we explore the historical context behind the establishment of debt ceilings and how they have evolved over time. We shed light on the reasons governments may hit their debt limit and the consequences that can arise when the ceiling is breached. Our analysis includes the potential effects on financial markets, credit ratings, borrowing costs, and public trust in the government's fiscal responsibility.

Additionally, we examine the intricate relationship between the debt ceiling and the political landscape. Through case studies and real-world examples, we explore how debates and negotiations surrounding debt ceiling increases or suspensions often become contentious and polarizing. We discuss the various strategies employed by governments to address the debt ceiling and the potential implications for the economy and citizens.

Throughout the video, we present clear graphics, charts, and data visualizations to enhance understanding and illustrate the key concepts discussed. We ensure that even viewers without prior knowledge of economics or government finance can follow along and grasp the significance of the debt ceiling in the broader financial ecosystem.

Whether you are a student, a concerned citizen, or a professional seeking to expand your knowledge of economic governance, "Understanding the Debt Ceiling: Navigating Fiscal Challenges" offers valuable insights and a comprehensive overview of this critical aspect of fiscal policy. Join us on this informative journey and gain a deeper understanding of the debt ceiling's impact on national economies and everyday lives.

A video by Abhiraj Rajadhyaksha & Niyati Mavinkurve

localized.title: Debt ceiling explained in Hindi | American Economic Crisis | Abhi and Niyu
localized.description:
In this video, Abhi and Niyu explain the Debt Ceiling crisis of USA and why America will never be like Sri Lanka.

#debtceiling #worldaffairs #abhiandniyu 

In our informative and engaging video, "Understanding the Debt Ceiling: Navigating Fiscal Challenges," we delve into one of the most critical aspects of economic governance: the debt ceiling. Join us on a journey through the complexities of national debt, government spending, and the mechanisms in place to manage these fiscal challenges.

With a clear and concise narrative, we break down the debt ceiling concept, explaining its purpose and implications. Our expert hosts provide a comprehensive overview of how the debt ceiling functions within the framework of a country's financial system and explore the practical effects it has on government operations and the economy at large.

As the video progresses, we explore the historical context behind the establishment of debt ceilings and how they have evolved over time. We shed light on the reasons governments may hit their debt limit and the consequences that can arise when the ceiling is breached. Our analysis includes the potential effects on financial markets, credit ratings, borrowing costs, and public trust in the government's fiscal responsibility.

Additionally, we examine the intricate relationship between the debt ceiling and the political landscape. Through case studies and real-world examples, we explore how debates and negotiations surrounding debt ceiling increases or suspensions often become contentious and polarizing. We discuss the various strategies employed by governments to address the debt ceiling and the potential implications for the economy and citizens.

Throughout the video, we present clear graphics, charts, and data visualizations to enhance understanding and illustrate the key concepts discussed. We ensure that even viewers without prior knowledge of economics or government finance can follow along and grasp the significance of the debt ceiling in the broader financial ecosystem.

Whether you are a student, a concerned citizen, or a professional seeking to expand your knowledge of economic governance, "Understanding the Debt Ceiling: Navigating Fiscal Challenges" offers valuable insights and a comprehensive overview of this critical aspect of fiscal policy. Join us on this informative journey and gain a deeper understanding of the debt ceiling's impact on national economies and everyday lives.

A video by Abhiraj Rajadhyaksha & Niyati Mavinkurve
